<li><strong>Multi-factor authentication</strong>: Implement multiple layers of authentication to protect sensitive accounts and prevent unauthorized access.</li>



<li><strong>Incident response plan</strong>: Develop a comprehensive plan to quickly detect, contain, and mitigate security incidents, minimizing their impact on your token ecosystem.</li>
</ol>



